quran[4{c,v,t}:
2,216,"tumhe jung ka hukum diya gaya hai aur woh tumhe nagawaar hai ho sakta hai ke aik cheez tumhe nagawaar ho aur wohi tumahray liye behtar ho aur ho sakta hai ke aik cheez tumhe pasand ho aur wohi tumahray liye buri ho Allah jaanta hai, tum nahi jantay"
2,217,"log puchhte hain mah haraam mein larna kaisa hai? kaho : iss mein lar na bohat bura hai, magar raah khuda se logon ko rokna aur Allah se kufar karna aur masjid haraam ka rasta khuda paraston par band karna aur haram ke rehne walon ko wahan se nikalna Allah ke nazdeek iss se bhi ziyada bura hai aur fitnah khonrizi se shadeed tar hai woh to tum se larray hi jayen ge hatta ke agar unn ka bas chalay, to tumhe iss deen se phira le jayen ( aur yeh khoob samajh lau ke ) tum mein se jo koi is deen se phiray ga aur kufar ki haalat mein jaan day ga, is ke aamaal duniya aur akhirat dono mein zaya ho jayen ge aisay sab log jahanumi hain aur hamesha jahannum hi mein rahen ge"
2,218,"bakhalaaf iss ke jo log imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne khuda ki raah mein apna ghar baar chorra aur jehaad kya hai, woh rehmat Ellahi ke jaaiz umeed waar hain aur Allah un ki lagzishon ko maaf karne wala aur apni rehmat se inhen nawazne wala hai"
2,219,"puchhte hain : sharaab aur juye ka kya hukum hai? kaho : un dono cheezon mein barri khaRabi hai agarchay un mein logon ke liye kuch munafe bhi hain, magar un ka gunah unn ke faiday se bohat ziyada hai puchhte hain : hum raah khuda mein kya kharch karen? kaho : jo kuch tumhari zaroorat se ziyada ho is terhan Allah tumahray liye saaf saaf ehkaam bayan karta hai, shayad ke tum duniya aur akhirat dono ki fikar karo"
